Interface TriangleModel

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractTriangleModel, AccidentTriangleModel, CalendarTriangleModel, DevelopmentTriangleModel
public interface TriangleModel

A triangle model is responsible for the layout of a Triangle within a widget.
